    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-03-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-03-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="569"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d569">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00112 European War 1939/4927</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Assistant Chief of the Division of Near Eastern
                        Affairs</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Villard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Chargé at Tangier</hi> (<persName
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Childs</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-03-18">March 18,
                            1942</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Rives</hi>: We have been greatly interested in your
                    telegram no. 116 of March 13, 1942, as well as all of your previous telegrams on
                    the subject thereof. The Department has been giving the most careful
                    consideration to the possibilities which you have outlined but at this date it
                    has not been possible to give you a definite answer.</p>
                <p>Just as soon as it is possible to do so, we shall communicate with you further.
                    In the meantime I wanted you to know that your telegrams have aroused the
                    greatest interest and are receiving all possible attention.</p>
                <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>H. S. <hi rend="smallcaps">Villard</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
